text: Ocotea uxpanapana is a species of plant in the family Lauraceae. It is a species of evergreen tree in the genus Ocotea. It is endemic to Veracruz state in eastern Mexico. ==References== uxpanapana Category:Endemic flora of Mexico Category:Flora of Veracruz Category:Trees of Mexico Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
